[h3 id=AboutThisGameAndMovie 
	"About this game and movie
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Inspector Blindson is a Flash game developed by Rakotilla. It follows the story of the titular Inspector Mr. Blindson, who's on a mission to save a man's life, only to find out that the man in question took the song 
	[em 
		"Pretty Fly for a White Guy
	]em
	" way too literally, shortly before being eaten by him.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This movie aims to find the correct tool and rescue the man as fast as possible, and it achieves that goal 6 seconds faster than 
