[h3 id=Mechanics 
	"Mechanics
	$LF
]h3
[dl 
	[dt 
		"Moving
	]dt
	[dd 
		" There no acceleration in this game, kinda. Still, whenever you see me hugging a wall, just know that I wasn't losing any time.
		$LF
		[dt 
			"Falling
		]dt
		[dd 
			" If you fall from a distance that's roughly 2/3rds of the screen, you die.
			$LF
			[dt 
				"Corner jumps
			]dt
			[dd 
				" You can stand on the corner of vertical spikes and flames, though, since movement is so limited, you can only do these in some places, not all of them.
				$LF
			]dd
		]dd
	]dd
]dl
[h3 id=InterestingLevels 
	"Interesting levels
	$LF
]h3
[dl 
	[dt 
		"Level 1
	]dt
	[dd 
		" I actually had to slightly manipulate my position in the bottom floor so that I didn't waste time by requiring an extra jump. If you see the RTA WR, you'll see the difference.
		$LF
		[dt 
			"Level 7
		]dt
		[dd 
			" By doing a relatively simple jump, you can skip grabbing the fireproof suit, saving some time.
			$LF
			[dt 
				"Level 17
			]dt
			[dd 
				" The SCUBA is roughly a second faster than the other safety equipment, seeing as you don't have to wait for platforms.
				$LF
				[dt 
					"Level 19
				]dt
				[dd 
					" Performing a corner jump, you can skip collecting the safety equipment, saving loads of time. If you're wondering, it's only possible to perform it on the outer side of the spikes, losing a little bit of time unfortunately.
					$LF
					[dt 
						"Level 23
					]dt
					[dd 
						" If you're wondering, if you try to complete the stage without collecting the TR-128 (which is slower btw), you won't be able to progress through the door.
						$LF
					]dd
				]dd
			]dd
		]dd
	]dd
]dl
